strings: <voice_0x01000C7A><se_high>Tree: I want to zoom! Now the king doesn't want to talk to anyone. Forgive those who hurt you.
<voice_0x01000C7B><se_high>Tree: As you know, since the death of Queen Sasha two years ago, nothing has changed.
<voice_0x01000C7C><se_high>Tree: If they are found dead... It is very important for the king to see the queen again.
<voice_0x01000C7D><se_high>Tree: ...When I was little, my grandmother told me stories. A Unique Story Unlike Any Other
<voice_0x01000C7E><se_high>Tree: I'm sure there must be a way to make any wish come true... but it's useless, I can't remember.
<voice_0x01000C7F><se_high>Tree: She wanted me to tell her when she arrived. But I'm too busy with the locks...
<voice_0x01000C80><se_high>Tree: Sorry, but I have a request.
<voice_0x01000C81><se_high>Tree: I want you to go to grandma's house. She lives in a house not far from the west side of the bridge.
<voice_0x01000C82><se_high>Tree: Can you ask him to tell you the ancient story of his blessing?
<voice_0x01000C83><se_high>Tree: Maybe just a fairy tale, but it is true if given the opportunity. I will do anything to help the king.
<voice_0x01000C84><se_high>Tree: I just want to ask, but there is a lot going on inside the palace. And I can't leave her alone...
<voice_0x01000C85><se_high>Tree: I'm counting on the help. My grandmother lives in a house next to the bridge to the west of Ascanta.
<voice_0x01000C86><se_high>Tree: I pray every day at church so that the king can be happy again. It's her request...help her...
